imary\" style><br></a></h5>\n                <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\">WhatsApp</span><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 20rem) / 28));\">:</b><br></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/+2975659535?text=Hello there! Pleasures In Aruba escorts is eager to answer your questions about our services and look forward to hearing from you.\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">+297 565 9535</a></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><br></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">Email:\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><a href=\"mailto:pleasureinaruba@hotmail.com\" class=\"text-primary\">pleasureinaruba@hotmail.com\n</a></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><a href=\"mailto:camiladearuba@gmail.com\" class=\"text-primary\">camiladearuba@gmail.com</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 mt-4\" mbr-if=\"showCopyright\">\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mb-0 mbr-fonts-style copyright align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".copyright\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                    © Copyright 2026&nbsp;<a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Pleasure In Aruba&nbsp;Escorts</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aruba\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">(AW)</a><br><a href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/privacy-terms-pleasure-in-aruba\" class=\"text-success text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Privacy Policy | Terms &amp; Conditions</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
