          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"gallery3\" group=\"Sliders & Galleries\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"cardsWidth\">\n            <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"6\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\">\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageHeight\" title=\"Height\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"autoSize && !(showButtons==false && showCardSubtitle==false && showCardTitle==false && showText==false)\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Spacing\" name=\"spacing\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"transparent\" title=\"Transparent BG\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsBg\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#353535\" condition=\"(transparent==false)\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" required>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#1f1e1e\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.1\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><a href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/Pleasure-in-Aruba-Trans-Escorts.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Pleasure In Aruba Trans Escorts</a>⚧</h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><div>\n</div><div><b>Pleasure In Aruba Escorts</b> provides the most discrete <b>TS Trans </b>escort experience in Aruba, with years in the business we've only got the most professional and experienced Trans escorts working for us.</div></h5>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n            \n            \n            <div class=\"item features-image сol-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}} active\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"item-img\">\n                        <a href=\"Victoria-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/pleasure-in-aruba-trans-escorts-02-victoria.webp\" alt=\"Pleasure In Aruba Trans Escort - Victoria\" title data-slide-to=\"0\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\"></a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                        <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">✬<a href=\"Victoria-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\" class=\"text-primary\"></a><a href=\"Victoria-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Victoria</a>✬</h5>\n                        <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-1\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">Sexy Trans Escort in Aruba</h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Hi, I am <a href=\"page15.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Victoria</a>, a sexy trans escort living in Aruba. I am friendly, private, and discreet. The ultimate fantasy for bisexual and straight men who want something different. I am your perfect girl to attend dinners with and shows and everything else in between!\n<br>\n<br>For the special men out there seeking a gorgeous trans escort, I have quite a surprise for you. I love doing what I do, and I believe it shows. Thanks for taking the time to read my profile. I cannot wait to meet up. Call me.<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"Victoria-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\">Victoria Gallery⚧</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-image сol-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}} active\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"item-img\">\n                        <a href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/Angelica-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/pleasure-in-aruba-ts-escorts-trans-angelica-03b.webp\" alt=\"Pleasure In Aruba Trans Escort - Angelica\" title data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\"></a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                        <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">✬<a href=\"Victoria-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\" class=\"text-primary\"></a><a href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/Angelica-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba\" class=\"text-primary\">Angelica</a>✬</h5>\n                        <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-1\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">Your Seductive TS Escort</h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Hi, I am <a href=\"page15.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Victoria</a>, a sexy trans escort living in Aruba. I am friendly, private, and discreet. The ultimate fantasy for bisexual and straight men who want something different. I am your perfect girl to attend dinners with and shows and everything else in between!\n<br>\n<br>For the special men out there seeking a gorgeous trans escort, I have quite a surprise for you. I love doing what I do, and I believe it shows. Thanks for taking the time to read my profile. I cannot wait to meet up. Call me.<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/Angelica-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba\">Angelica Gallery⚧</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
