howCardSubtitle\"><b><i>Your ultimate temptation, soft and dangerously irresistible.</i></b></h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Whether you’re winding down from a long day or a fun night out, I’m here in Aruba to offer you refined relaxation, sensual pleasure, and unforgettable moments.&nbsp;Call Now to experience pleasure you won't forget.<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"https://pleasureinarubaescort.netlify.app/catalina-pleasure-in-aruba-escorts.html\">💜Catalina Gallery</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
