          "_name": "gallery1",
          "_sourceTheme": "commercem4",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"mbr-gallery mbr-slider-carousel\" group=\"Sliders & Gallery\" plugins=\"Masonry,Slider,BootstrapCarouselSwipe,Gallery,VimeoVideo\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width Gallery\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" inline>\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" inline>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Items Overlay Color 1\" name=\"overlayColor1\" value=\"#232323\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Items Gradient Overlay\" name=\"gradientOverlay\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Items Overlay Color 2\" name=\"overlayColor2\" value=\"#1f1e1e\" condition=\"gradientOverlay\">\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Items Overlay Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacityItem\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" inline>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Tags Color\" name=\"tagsColor\" value=\"#232323\">\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#1e1d1d\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"gallery\" title=\"Gallery\" name=\"gallery\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style pb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">✬<a href=\"Angelica-Trans-TS-Escort-Aruba.html\" class=\"text-primary\">Angelica Best of Both Worlds TS Escort</a>✬</h3>\n        <h2 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title,.mbr-gallery-filter ul\" mbr-class=\"{'pb-4':!gallery__filter}\"><div>I am <b>Angelica</b>, your seductive, <b>TS escort</b>.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">I’m new in Aruba and would be happy to meet you. I’m intelligent, sexy, and with me, you will surely reach your fetish and high level of passion.&nbsp;</span></div><br><div>For those with a more daring side, I also offer the opportunity to explore your own submission under my attentive guidance. Wherever we meet, I promise a connection worth remembering. <i>I cannot wait to meet up. <a href=\"https://pleasuresinaruba.com/pleasure-in-aruba-contact-us\" class=\"text-primary\">Contact us</a>.</i></div><div><br></div><div>Location: Aruba\n</div><div>Services: Male, Female, Couples\n</div><div>(<a href=\"https://wa.me/+2975659535?text=Hello there! Pleasures In Aruba escorts is eager to answer your questions about our services and look forward to hearing from you.\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Please contact me for information about my services</a>)</div></h2>\n    </div> \n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"col-left-gallery\" mbr-gallery=\"gallery\" mbr-gallery-spacing=\"1\"></div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
